Text: China announced a range of US goods to be exempted from 25 percent extra tariffs put in place earlier, as China seeks to ease the impact from the trade war without lifting charges on major agricultural items such as soybeans and pork.
Cause: China seeks to ease the impact from the trade war without lifting charges on major agricultural items such as soybeans and pork.
